# Hugo's generated site output — rebuilt from content/layouts on every build, never hand-edited
public/
# Hugo's resource cache (processed images, etc.) — regenerated automatically, machine-specific
resources/
# Hugo dev-server lock file — local/transient, recreated on each `hugo server` run
.hugo_build.lock
# Per-machine Claude Code permission allowlist — differs between Windows and Linux devs (see CLAUDE.md)
.claude/settings.json
# Per-machine Claude Code local overrides — same reason as settings.json above
.claude/settings.local.json
# Draft ToS pulled out of content/posts/ but kept locally for reference, not meant to ship
deprecated-dbj-systems-service-agreement.md
